data.description:
Welcome to your dream WATERFRONT RETREAT in the World-Renowned Three Sisters Springs area! This custom-built 5-bedroom 3-bathroom POOL home with a 2-car garage provides luxury and comfort at every turn. Situated on an 85ft Fresh Spring Canal leading directly to the Gulf of Mexico, you'll revel in the breathtaking views of the waterway and the Manatees right from your expansive 36 x 28ft deck. Step out the back door onto your covered lanai and relax in your expansive 8ft deep pool-the perfect spot for relaxing and entertaining after a long day on the water.
Inside the home exudes elegance with a remodeled kitchen, new appliances and travertine floors throughout. The open family room features a tray ceiling and crown molding, creating an inviting space for gatherings. With Sliding glass doors from every area of the home providing seamless access to the pool area, indoor-outdoor living is effortless. For added convenience a 25ft side yard offers ample space for trailer parking, catering to your adventurous spirit. Plus, with a new roof and 18 SEER A/C installed in 2017 you can enjoy peace of mind knowing that your home is equipped with modern amenities and upgrades.
